---
import Card from '../Card.astro'
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-4" title="What I do">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
    <p class="pt-1 text-sm font-light">📍 Cologne, Germany</p>

    <p class="pt-1 text-sm font-light">
      Most interested in problems where software engineering, infrastructure,
      data, and organisational processes intersect — especially where the
      challenge is making complex systems a joy to use while remaining
      economically real.
    </p>

    <div>
      <p class="pt-1 text-sm font-semibold">What I work on</p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc pt-1 text-sm font-light">
        <li>LLM systems & semantic search</li>
        <li>Data platforms on Kubernetes & AWS</li>
        <li>Regulated enterprise AI (insurance, finance)</li>
        <li>Process automation & integration</li>
        <li>GenAI, traditional ML, and orchestration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="pt-1 text-sm font-light">
      Earlier highlights include the
      <a
        href="https://codein.withgoogle.com/archive/2018/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="text-primary underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
        >Google Code-In Grand Prize</a
      > (2018, one of 26 worldwide) and being employee #1 at a YC SS21 startup
      that became Zepto.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
